rofit organization that supports weeklong surgical medical mission trips to honduras for usbased physicians nurses clinical and nonclinical personnel to provide free surgical care to people who cannot afford or access care the program partnered with the holy family surgery center an ambulatory surgery center located near tegucigalpa honduras on the grounds of a  acre orphanage part of the nuestros pequeños hermanos network with more than  children referencesedit  httpwwwbeckersasccomascturnaroundsideastoimproveperformancethingstoknowaboutofbiggestasccompaniesinthemarkettodayamsurghcasurgerypartnersscauspihtml  scai  form k wwwsecgov sec   httpinvestorscasurgerycomreleasedetailcfmreleaseid  httpfilesshareholdercomdownloadsamdacklxxbccebfefacfcscaglossyannualreportbookmarkedpdfpdf  httpwwwbeckersasccomascturnaroundsideastoimproveperformancethingstoknowaboutofbiggestasccompaniesinthemarkettodayamsurghcasurgerypartnersscauspihtml  httpinvestorscasurgerycomreleasedetailcfmreleaseid  httpsfinanceyahoocomquotescailtr  httpwwwunitedhealthgroupcomnewsroomarticlesfeedoptumscaoptumcareaspx  httpwwwunitedhealthgroupcomnewsroomarticlesfeedoptumsurgicalcareaffiliatesaspxr  “surgical care affiliate” google finance httpswwwgooglecomfinanceqscaieiqhkfvhzecysaarrjwaq  httpwwwomenbookscomomenreportsomenreportstennesseespoliticalhealthcaremazehtml  httpswwwbloombergcomresearchstockssnapshotsnapshotarticleasptickersgr  httpwwwavondalepartnersllccompeoplejoelcgordon  httpnashvillepostcomnewsnashvillenowandthenendingsandbeginnings  httpwwwcompanyhistoriescomhealthsouthcorporationcompanyhistoryhtml  httpwwwsecinfocomdmxbabhtmwwwsecinfocomdmxbabhtm  httpwwwsecinfocomdmxbabhtmwwwsecinfocomdmxbabhtm  httpwwwavondalepartnersllccomaboutadvisoryboard  httpwwwavondalepartnersllccomaboutadvisoryboard  international directory of company histories vol  st james press   httpswwwbloombergcomresearchstocksprivatepersonasppersonidprivcapid  httpwwwbeckersasccomascturnaroundsideastoimproveperformancethin